OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPerhaps rather cloudy to start,
OL,6,Fsoon clearing to give lengthy sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Cloud may linger near coasts.
OL,8,FWarm or very warm inland, cooler near
OL,9,Fcoasts especially in the breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAnother cloudy start before
OL,12,Flifting and burning back towards the
OL,13,Fcoast, leaving sunny spells for most.
OL,14,FCloud returns in the evening but not
OL,15,Fas extensive as previous nights.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FMorning cloud will burn back
OL,18,Fto the coast during the morning to
OL,19,Fgive sunny spells. Temperatures around
OL,20,For a little above average. Breezy
OL,21,Fnortheasterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
